### 基础健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### 获取所有用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users

### 根据ID获取用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/1

### 创建新用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三",
  "email": "zhangsan@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 更新用户信息
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三更新",
  "email": "zhangsan_updated@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138001"
}

### 部分更新用户
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三部分更新"
}

### 删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/1

### 用户列表分页查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users?page=1&limit=10&name=张

### 测试验证错误 - 缺少必填字段
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email"
}

### 测试验证错误 - 邮箱格式错误
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试用户",
  "email": "invalid-email-format"
}

### 测试404错误 - 用户不存在
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/999999

### 环境变量示例（可以在设置中配置）
# @hostname = localhost
# @port = 8080
# @baseUrl = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

### 使用环境变量的请求示例
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users

### 带有认证头的请求示例（如果项目后续添加认证）
# GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
# Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### 文件上传示例（如果项目后续支持文件上传）
# POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/1/avatar
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
#
# --boundary
